      "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body": "There is a second generator in [secp256k1-zkp](https://github.com/elementsproject/secp256k1-zkp) which is our fork of libsecp with support for Pedersen commitments, rangeproofs, etc. Because this library is a supporting library for Bitcoin, which currently does not use Pedersen commitments anywhere, it doesn't contain the extra modules which would make use of this generator.\r\n\r\nIf you have a Bitcoin-relevant use case for Pedersen commitments I think a case could be made to bring this support into libsecp, but I'm not aware of one.",
